latestPosts.caption:
Work shouldn’t feel like a battle on your not-so-great days ❌

Women go through different phases in their lives—physically and mentally—which take time to adjust to and get comfortable with. It could be your first day of periods, a low morning, a sleepless night with your child, or just a normal, random, confusing day!

We understand the need for space—to take a break, breathe for a moment, and return with renewed energy.

So, we did something… 🤠

We introduced the De-Caff Comfort & NO-JUDGEMENT Room—a space exclusively for our women to rest, recharge, or simply take a break from the many things life throws at them. With recliners, hot bags, chocolates, books, and cozy couches, we aimed to bring the feeling of home into the workplace. A place where they can GO & CHILL, without being judged. 🤓

At Pep Brands, every day is about creating a workplace where women feel valued, cared for, and understood 🫂.

To all the powerful women at Pep—this one’s for you! ❤️

And yes—Happy Women’s Day, every day!

latestPosts.caption:
Guys, the sale has been extended! 🥳

PS. Sorry supply team. Please drop condolences for our supply team below. They need it 🥹

Anddd that’s how we are kickstarting our 8th Birthday! 🎉🥳

It feels like we are right back at year one - building from the ground up. From those late nights fine-tuning our tech integrations, to the never-ending D2C strategy meetings, prepping marketing assets, and ensuring our dispatch team is set to deliver on every promise. Every step, every detail - big or small - carries that same rush, those same nerves, and the same thrill as when we first started.

These events are not just Big Sale Events, but opportunities to push the limits, learn new skills and unlearn some old ways, integrating the larger group for a common goal & celebrating lots of small wins, along with big ones.

Even after sleepless nights that come with being a mom, walking into the office and seeing our teams pour their hearts into our 8th anniversary - the biggest sale of the year - instantly washes away all the exhaustion. Sharing a glimpse of multiple verticals, working to achieve our common goal 🙌🏻

We’re beyond excited to kick off mCaffeine’s 8th Golden Birthday Bash! 🎉 
And this year, we’ve got even bigger, better surprises lined up. Stay tuned! 😉

We are just getting started!
